 src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"fixed inset-x-0 top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#05070A]/70 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-20 max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 md:h-28 md:px-8\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center md:self-end md:pb-4\"><img alt=\"3rd-AI\" width=\"140\" height=\"36\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;width:clamp(140px, 14vw, 170px);height:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-12 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 md:flex\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">About</a></nav><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"hidden rounded-full border border-cyan-400/60 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-black md:block\">Technical Briefing</a><button class=\"flex h-10 w-10 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span></button></div></header><div class=\"fixed inset-x-0 top-20 z-40 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#05070A]/95 backdrop-blur-xl transition-all duration-300 md:hidden\n          opacity-0 -translate-y-2 pointer-events-none\"><nav class=\"flex flex-col px-6 py-6 gap-1\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">About</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"mt-4 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/60 px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-all hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-black\">Technical Briefing</a></nav></div><main class=\"bg-black\"><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-8 pt-56 pb-24\"><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-400\">Legal</p><h1 class=\"text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500\">Last updated: July 2026 · 3rd-AI Limited · Company No. 16341261</p><div class=\"mt-16 space-y-12 text-base leading-8 text-slate-400\"><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">1. Who we are</h2><p>3rd-AI Limited is a private limited company registered in England and Wales (Company No. 16341261), with its registered office at 3 Assembly Square, Cardiff, Wales CF10 4, GB.</p><p class=\"mt-4\">We operate the website at <span class=\"text-cyan-400\">www.3rd-ai.com</span>. For any privacy-related queries, contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:info@3rd-ai.com\" class=\"text-cyan-400 hover:opacity-70\">info@3rd-ai.com</a>.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">2. What data we collect</h2><p>We collect personal data only when you voluntarily submit our contact form. This may include:</p><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Full name</li><li>Work email address</li><li>Company name</li><li>Inquiry type and message content</li></ul><p class=\"mt-4\">We do not use cookies for tracking, advertising, or analytics. We do not collect any data passively from visitors to this website.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">3. How we use your data</h2><p>We use the information you submit solely to:</p><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Respond to your inquiry</li><li>Arrange technical briefings or follow-up discussions</li></ul><p class=\"mt-4\">We do not use your data for marketing without your explicit consent, and we do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for their own purposes.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">4. How your data is processed</h2><p>Contact form submissions are processed via<!-- --> <span class=\"text-white font-medium\">Formspree</span> (formspree.io), a third-party form handling service. Formspree receives and forwards your submission to us by email. By submitting the contact form, your data will be processed by Formspree in accordance with their privacy policy, available at<!-- --> <a href=\"https://formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-cyan-400 hover:opacity-70\">formspree.io/legal/privacy-policy</a>.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">5. Legal basis for processing</h2><p>We process your personal data on the basis of<!-- --> <span class=\"text-white\">legitimate interests</span> — specifically, to respond to business inquiries you have initiated. Where required, we rely on your <span class=\"text-white\">consent</span> as the legal basis.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">6. Data retention</h2><p>We retain your contact information only for as long as necessary to respond to your inquiry and maintain a reasonable record of correspondence — typically no longer than 24 months. You may request deletion at any time.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">7. Your rights</h2><p>Under UK GDPR, you have the right to:</p><ul class=\"mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-6\"><li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li><li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li><li>Request deletion of your data</li><li>Object to or restrict processing</li><li>Lodge a complaint with the ICO at<!-- --> <a href=\"https://ico.org.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-cyan-400 hover:opacity-70\">ico.org.uk</a></li></ul><p class=\"mt-4\">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:info@3rd-ai.com\" class=\"text-cyan-400 hover:opacity-70\">info@3rd-ai.com</a>.</p></div><div><h2 class=\"mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-white\">8. Changes to this policy</h2><p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. We encourage you to review this page periodically.</p></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-white/5 bg-[#05070A] py-12\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between\"><div><a href=\"/\" class=\"inline-flex items-center self-end\"><img alt=\"3rd-AI\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;width:120px;height:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Ambient Intelligence for connected environments.</p></div><nav class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-10 gap-y-3 text-sm text-slate-500\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">About</a><a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Privacy Policy</a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/3rd-ai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">LinkedIn</a></nav></div><div class=\"my-8 h-px bg-white/5\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs text-slate-600\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> 3rd-AI Limited. All rights reserved.</p><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-2xl leading-5 md:mt-0\">Projected figures are based on modelled deployment scenarios and do not represent guaranteed outcomes. Statements regarding future capabilities are forward-looking and subject to change.</p><p class=\"leading-5\">3rd-AI Limited · Registered in England &amp; Wales · Company No. 16341261</p></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1guoti84v2fh3.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[7988,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3vxl_ykt3m0uw.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n12:I[68027,[\\\"